data.description: Truly move-in ready & recently updated 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bath home in Bristol Club. This home has remarkably high ceilings & remote-controlled solar shades on the upper windows. Recently updated & meticulously well-kept. Some Updates include wood flooring throughout the downstairs, stairs & upstairs hallway, and new designer carpeting in the bedrooms. The kitchen has custom-crafted wood ceilings, quartz countertops, Carrara marble backsplash, wood cabinetry & newer Stainless-Steel appliances. Impact glass windows and doors throughout. 5-ton Lennox A/C installed in 2023 with UV Lighting. Upgraded Landscaping in front & backyard. Phantom Screens & Retractable Awning in Lanai and Extended Patio. The garage has a new hurricane-rated & insulated garage door, a wall-mounted A/C & epoxy flooring All Closets boast California Closet built-ins., Master Bathroom has been updated with large newly tiled shower with bench & frameless glass doors. The garage has new hurricane rated & insulated garage door, a wall-mounted A/C & epoxy flooring.
